title: JavaScript

I used to use a little JavaScript when it was new. It outgrew me.

I don't want to use JavaScript. //Everyone// else already does it. I can't swing a dead cat without hitting a "Full-stack JavaScript Developer" and it bores me to tears. On the other hand, it's fast enough, easy enough, and available enough to be the most immediately useful tool I could choose. So there's that.